	dprr:hasNoteText "Tr. pl. desig. for 42. In MRR 2.359, reverse the order of the words in the name. See CIL 9.5560, the name L. Hostilius Tullus. (TJC) See Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 117-RP 2.595; Shackleton Bailey, Studies 45.\n" ;
